name: Luminous Wave
description:
The ridged gills of closely clumped fruiting bodies of the bioluminescent Bitter Oyster colony are exposed and are gently lit by the ambient light at the forest edge. (Panellus stipticus)

2019. Nikon D3500, 55-200mm Lens.

Photographed in situ, without the use of artificial lighting or staging. Photoshop only used for resizing.

1024x685 300dpi jpeg
